    &chap.plist;
    &chap.pkginstall;
    &chap.fixes;
    &chap.gnome;
    &chap.submit;
    &chap.devfaq;




    The pkgsrc infrastructure internals


This part of the guide deals with everything
	from the infrastructure that is behind the interfaces described
	in the developer's guide. A casual package maintainer should not
	need anything from this part.

    &chap.infr.design;
    &chap.regression;
    &chap.porting;



